{"tid":1359827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康再論反送中 華春瑩：閉嘴","createTime":"2019-07-24T08:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T08:27:21.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"544da83043c26178cde77cf5aec304a0b746dbb2","tid":1359827,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:22:25.000Z","msg":"前港督彭定康再次就本港因修訂《逃犯條例》觸發的衝突表態，贊成設立獨立委員會調查連串衝突。在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩回應指出，中方的立場非常的堅定，堅決反對任何外部勢力企圖干預香港的內部事務，希望他們能儘早在這個問題上閉嘴、收手。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩稱，彭定康選擇性地失明，選擇性地發聲，避而不談衝擊立法會和中聯辦大樓事件，他的真實意圖是昭然若揭的。<br />\n<br />\n對於部分國家對港發出旅遊警示，華春瑩認為，大家應該團結起來共同維護好香港的安全與秩序，重新讓香港這顆東方之珠煥發出璀璨的光芒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2199262/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2199262%2F&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe9xiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=146fe126\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2199262/</a>"},{"pid":"acbc5dcc979a00f8a40e3208660af10cec8f1ffd","tid":1359827,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c061fbeed9ee385081f2253efe50e283f7810c2b","tid":1359827,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}